= Angelo Rodio  | Linköping University |  Biography

== Short Bio
\n
I earned a BSc in Computer Engineering and an MSc in Telecommunications from [https://poliba.esse3.cineca.it/Guide/PaginaCorso.do?corso_id=10016 Polytechnic University of Bari], Italy, in 2018 and 2020, respectively.\n
Through a double diploma program, I obtained an M.Sc. in Computer Engineering from [https://ubinet.univ-cotedazur.fr Université Côte D'Azur], France.\n
I defended my PhD thesis on [https://www.theses.fr/s318701 "Client Heterogeneity in Federated Learning Systems"], at Inria, France, on July 3rd, 2024, supervised by [http://www-sop.inria.fr/members/Giovanni.Neglia/ Dr. Giovanni Neglia].

For more details, please refer to my [pdfs/CV.pdf CV] (updated Sep. 2023).

